OL,3,CHealth chief calls for 'reset' as he
OL,4,Cbattles #600m budget deficit
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland's new health chief
OL,7,Fhas called for a complete reset of the
OL,8,Fhealthcare system as he battles with a
OL,9,F#600m budget deficit.
OL,11,FMike Farrar says he expects
OL,12,Funprecedented savings to be made to
OL,13,Fplug the gap, with potentially up to
OL,14,F#300m of cuts to be found.
OL,16,FA third of that black hole is money to
OL,17,Fimplement pay awards.
