OL,3,CHealth chief calls for 'reset' as he
OL,4,Cbattles #600m budget deficit
OL,6,FThe new permanent secretary says he
OL,7,Fdoesn't have the #200m in his budget
OL,8,Fand has had to ask for more money from
OL,9,Fthe Executive after a ministerial
OL,10,Fdirection.
OL,12,F"Undoubtedly we've had some very, very
OL,13,Fsignificant challenge," Mr Farrar told
OL,14,FUTV.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
