OL,3,CHealth chief calls for 'reset' as he
OL,4,Cbattles #600m budget deficit
OL,6,F"But I'm actually very optimistic
OL,7,Fbecause I believe that if we can work
OL,8,Four way through this - we need to
OL,9,Freset the way healthcare is delivered
OL,10,Fin Northern Ireland - but if we can do
OL,11,Fthat, genuinely, I think can have one
OL,12,Fof the best health and care systems in
OL,13,Fthe world."
OL,15,FMike Farrar took up the position of
OL,16,Fpermanent secretary of the Health
OL,17,FDepartment in mid April, having
OL,18,Fpreviously held senior positions
OL,19,Fwithin the NHS in England.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
