OL,3,CHealth chief calls for 'reset' as he
OL,4,Cbattles #600m budget deficit
OL,6,FHe said while there are several big
OL,7,Fimmediate challenges in the health
OL,8,Fservice, he is optimistic about its
OL,9,Ffuture.
OL,11,F"The biggest challenge at the moment
OL,12,Fis money," Mr Farrar said.
OL,14,F"I inherited a budget at the beginning
OL,15,Fof the year, which has a #600m
OL,16,Fdeficit, and whilst we are working our
OL,17,Fsocks off to try and close that, to
OL,18,Ftry and do that in year in a cashable
OL,19,Fway is very difficult.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
