OL,3,CHealth chief calls for 'reset' as he
OL,4,Cbattles #600m budget deficit
OL,6,F"As you're probably aware, we're
OL,7,Flooking at how we can afford the pay
OL,8,Faward that people want to pay, and at
OL,9,Fthe moment that's looking difficult.
OL,11,F"The pay amounts to #200m.
OL,13,F"The assumptions had been from
OL,14,FTreasury that it would be about 2.8% -
OL,15,Fprofessionals, which includes the
OL,16,Fnurses, came in at 3.6%, and the
OL,17,Fdoctors came in at 4%, so that's added
OL,18,Fanother #47m to our deficit."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
