OL,3,CHealth chief calls for 'reset' as he
OL,4,Cbattles #600m budget deficit
OL,6,FMr Farrar continued: "So we're
OL,7,Fobviously looking at cost savings, we
OL,8,Fcan't overspend so I need to make sure
OL,9,Fthat our trusts are doing their bit.
OL,11,F"As we stand I think I can see where
OL,12,Faround half of that is covered by what
OL,13,Fwe have by way of savings in the
OL,14,Ftrusts, and we're trying to do that in
OL,15,Fa way that doesn't jeopardize care.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/7
