OL,3,CHealth chief calls for 'reset' as he
OL,4,Cbattles #600m budget deficit
OL,6,F"We're trying to do that in a way that
OL,7,Factually is more effective and in some
OL,8,Fcases we can actually improve care, I
OL,9,Fwould argue, but at the moment I'm
OL,10,Fonly halfway there and the pay awards
OL,11,Fcome early in the year.
OL,13,F"And so that #200m, I've had to say
OL,14,FI'm sorry, we don't have that as yet
OL,15,Fin our budget, we can't find that."
